{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Rom|9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":9,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":1,"text":"I speak the truth in Christ —I am not lying; my conscience testifies to me through the Holy Spirit —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":2,"text":"that I have great sorrow and unceasing anguish in my heart.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":3,"text":"For I could wish that I myself were cursed and cut off from Christ for the benefit of my brothers and sisters, my own flesh and blood.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":4,"text":"They are Israelites, and to them belong the adoption, the glory, the covenants, the giving of the law, the temple service, and the promises.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":5,"text":"The ancestors are theirs, and from them, by physical descent, came the Christ, who is God over all, praised forever. Amen.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":6,"text":"Now it is not as though the word of God has failed, because not all who are descended from Israel are Israel.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":7,"text":"Neither is it the case that all of Abraham’s children are his descendants. On the contrary, your offspring will be traced through Isaac.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":8,"text":"That is, it is not the children by physical descent who are God’s children, but the children of the promise are considered to be the offspring.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":9,"text":"For this is the statement of the promise: At this time I will come, and Sarah will have a son.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":10,"text":"And not only that, but Rebekah conceived children through one man, our father Isaac.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":11,"text":"For though her sons had not been born yet or done anything good or bad, so that God’s purpose according to election might stand —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":12,"text":"not from works but from the one who calls —she was told, The older will serve the younger.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":13,"text":"As it is written: I have loved Jacob, but I have hated Esau.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":14,"text":"What should we say then? Is there injustice with God? Absolutely not!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":15,"text":"For he tells Moses, I will show mercy to whom I will show mercy, and I will have compassion on whom I will have compassion.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":16,"text":"So then, it does not depend on human will or effort but on God who shows mercy.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":17,"text":"For the Scripture tells Pharaoh, I raised you up for this reason so that I may display my power in you and that my name may be proclaimed in the whole earth.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":18,"text":"So then, he has mercy on whom he wants to have mercy and he hardens whom he wants to harden.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":19,"text":"You will say to me, therefore, “Why then does he still find fault? For who resists his will?”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":20,"text":"On the contrary, who are you, a human being, to talk back to God? Will what is formed say to the one who formed it, “Why did you make me like this?”","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":21,"text":"Or has the potter no right over the clay, to make from the same lump one piece of pottery for honor and another for dishonor?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":22,"text":"And what if God, wanting to display his wrath and to make his power known, endured with much patience objects of wrath prepared for destruction?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":23,"text":"And what if he did this to make known the riches of his glory on objects of mercy that he prepared beforehand for glory —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":24,"text":"on us, the ones he also called, not only from the Jews but also from the Gentiles?","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":25,"text":"As it also says in Hosea,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":26,"text":"And it will be in the place where they were told,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":27,"text":"But Isaiah cries out concerning Israel,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":28,"text":"since the Lord will execute his sentence","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":29,"text":"And just as Isaiah predicted:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":30,"text":"What should we say then? Gentiles, who did not pursue righteousness, have obtained righteousness —namely the righteousness that comes from faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":31,"text":"But Israel, pursuing the law of righteousness, has not achieved the righteousness of the law.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:32","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":32,"text":"Why is that? Because they did not pursue it by faith, but as if it were by works. They stumbled over the stumbling stone.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:33","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":9,"verse":33,"text":"As it is written,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":9,"paragraphStarts":[1,6,14,19,26,27,28,29,30],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Israel’s Rejection of Christ"},{"beforeVerse":6,"text":"God’s Gracious Election of Israel"},{"beforeVerse":14,"text":"God’s Selection Is Just"},{"beforeVerse":30,"text":"Israel’s Present State"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I speak the truth in Christ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:9","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:10","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:20","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 2:7","book":"1Ti","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" —I am not lying; my conscience testifies to me through the Holy Spirit "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or testifying with me by the Holy Spirit"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:9","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"2Co 11:10","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":10},{"label":"Gl 1:20","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":20},{"label":"1Tm 2:7","book":"1Ti","chapter":2,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or testifying with me by the Holy Spirit"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"that I have great sorrow and unceasing anguish in my heart. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I could wish "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 32:32","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":32,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" that I myself were cursed "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:3","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:22","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:8","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:9","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and cut off "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit to be anathema"},{"kind":"text","text":" from Christ for the benefit of my brothers and sisters, my own flesh and blood. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 32:32","book":"Exo","chapter":32,"verse":32},{"label":"1Co 12:3","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":3},{"label":"1Co 16:22","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":22},{"label":"Gl 1:8","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"Gl 1:9","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit to be anathema"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They are Israelites, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:6","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and to them belong the adoption, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 4:22","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:15","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" the glory, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 40:34","book":"Exo","chapter":40,"verse":34,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 8:11","book":"1Ki","chapter":8,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 1:28","book":"Ezk","chapter":1,"verse":28,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:5","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":5,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" the covenants, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 17:2","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":2,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 29:14","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":14,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:72","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":72,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:25","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":25,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:12","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"text","text":" the giving of the law, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 4:13","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":13,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 147:19","book":"Psa","chapter":147,"verse":19,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"text","text":" the temple service, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 7:6","book":"Deu","chapter":7,"verse":6,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 14:1","book":"Deu","chapter":14,"verse":1,"letter":"p"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:1","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"q"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:6","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":6,"letter":"r"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the promises. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:39","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":39,"letter":"s"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:32","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":32,"letter":"t"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:12","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"u"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:6","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":6},{"label":"Ex 4:22","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":22},{"label":"Rm 8:15","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":15},{"label":"Ex 40:34","book":"Exo","chapter":40,"verse":34},{"label":"1Kg 8:11","book":"1Ki","chapter":8,"verse":11},{"label":"Ezk 1:28","book":"Ezk","chapter":1,"verse":28},{"label":"Heb 9:5","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":5},{"label":"Gn 17:2","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":2},{"label":"Dt 29:14","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":14},{"label":"Lk 1:72","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":72},{"label":"Ac 3:25","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":25},{"label":"Eph 2:12","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":12},{"label":"Dt 4:13","book":"Deu","chapter":4,"verse":13},{"label":"Ps 147:19","book":"Psa","chapter":147,"verse":19},{"label":"Dt 7:6","book":"Deu","chapter":7,"verse":6},{"label":"Dt 14:1","book":"Deu","chapter":14,"verse":1},{"label":"Heb 9:1","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":1},{"label":"Heb 9:6","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":6},{"label":"Ac 2:39","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":39},{"label":"Ac 13:32","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":32},{"label":"Eph 2:12","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The ancestors are theirs, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:13","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:28","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":28,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and from them, by physical descent, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit them, according to the flesh"},{"kind":"text","text":" came the Christ, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 1:1–16","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:3","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" who is God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 2:9","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" over all, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:16–19","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" praised forever. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Or the Messiah, the one who is over all, the God who is blessed forever, or Messiah. God, who is over all, be blessed forever"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:25","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":25,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" Amen."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 3:13","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"Rm 11:28","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":28},{"label":"Mt 1:1–16","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 1:3","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Jn 1:1","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Col 2:9","book":"Col","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Col 1:16–19","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Rm 1:25","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit them, according to the flesh"},{"marker":4,"text":"Or the Messiah, the one who is over all, the God who is blessed forever, or Messiah. God, who is over all, be blessed forever"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now it is not as though the word of God has failed, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 23:19","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" because not all who are descended from Israel are Israel. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:47","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":47,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:28–29","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 6:16","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 23:19","book":"Num","chapter":23,"verse":19},{"label":"Jn 1:47","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":47},{"label":"Rm 2:28–29","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":28},{"label":"Gl 6:16","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Neither is it the case that all of Abraham’s children are his descendants. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit seed"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":33,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 4:23","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" On the contrary, your offspring will be traced"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit called"},{"kind":"text","text":" through Isaac."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 21:12","book":"Gen","chapter":21,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 21:12","book":"Gen","chapter":21,"verse":12,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:18","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":18,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 8:33","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":33},{"label":"Jn 8:39","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":39},{"label":"Gl 4:23","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":23},{"label":"Gn 21:12","book":"Gen","chapter":21,"verse":12},{"label":"Gn 21:12","book":"Gen","chapter":21,"verse":12},{"label":"Heb 11:18","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit seed"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit called"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"That is, it is not the children by physical descent "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit children of the flesh"},{"kind":"text","text":" who are God’s children, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:14","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" but the children of the promise "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:13","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:29","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":29,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 4:28","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":28,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:11","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":11,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" are considered to be the offspring. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:14","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 4:13","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":13},{"label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16},{"label":"Gl 3:29","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":29},{"label":"Gl 4:28","book":"Gal","chapter":4,"verse":28},{"label":"Heb 11:11","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit children of the flesh"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For this is the statement of the promise: At this time I will come, and Sarah will have a son."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:10","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:14","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:10","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:14","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":14,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 18:10","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":10},{"label":"Gn 18:14","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":14},{"label":"Gn 18:10","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":10},{"label":"Gn 18:14","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And not only that, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:3","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" but Rebekah conceived children "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 25:21","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" through one man, our father Isaac. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 5:3","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":3},{"label":"Gn 25:21","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For though her sons had not been born yet or done anything good or bad, so that God’s purpose according to election might stand "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:17","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 4:17","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":17},{"label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"not from works but from the one who calls —she was told, The older will serve the younger."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 25:23","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 25:23","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 25:23","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":23},{"label":"Gn 25:23","book":"Gen","chapter":25,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As it is written: I have loved Jacob, but I have hated Esau."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mal 1:2–3","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mal 1:2–3","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mal 1:2–3","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"Mal 1:2–3","book":"Mal","chapter":1,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What should we say then? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:5","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Is there injustice with God? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 19:7","book":"2Ch","chapter":19,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:11","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" Absolutely not! "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 20:16","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 3:5","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"2Ch 19:7","book":"2Ch","chapter":19,"verse":7},{"label":"Rm 2:11","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"Lk 20:16","book":"Luk","chapter":20,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For he tells Moses, I will show mercy to whom I will show mercy, and I will have compassion on whom I will have compassion."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 33:19","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 33:19","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 33:19","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":19},{"label":"Ex 33:19","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So then, it does not depend on human will or effort "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:2","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" but on God who shows mercy. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:8","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gl 2:2","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":2},{"label":"Eph 2:8","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For the Scripture tells Pharaoh, I raised you up for this reason so that I may display my power in you and that my name may be proclaimed in the whole earth."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 9:16","book":"Exo","chapter":9,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 9:16","book":"Exo","chapter":9,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 9:16","book":"Exo","chapter":9,"verse":16},{"label":"Ex 9:16","book":"Exo","chapter":9,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So then, he has mercy on whom he wants to have mercy and he hardens whom he wants to harden. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 4:21","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 7:3","book":"Exo","chapter":7,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 9:12","book":"Exo","chapter":9,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 10:20","book":"Exo","chapter":10,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 10:27","book":"Exo","chapter":10,"verse":27,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 11:10","book":"Exo","chapter":11,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 14:4","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":4,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 14:7","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":7,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 2:30","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":30,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 11:20","book":"Jos","chapter":11,"verse":20,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:40","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":40,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:7","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":7,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:25","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":25,"letter":"m"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 4:21","book":"Exo","chapter":4,"verse":21},{"label":"Ex 7:3","book":"Exo","chapter":7,"verse":3},{"label":"Ex 9:12","book":"Exo","chapter":9,"verse":12},{"label":"Ex 10:20","book":"Exo","chapter":10,"verse":20},{"label":"Ex 10:27","book":"Exo","chapter":10,"verse":27},{"label":"Ex 11:10","book":"Exo","chapter":11,"verse":10},{"label":"Ex 14:4","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":4},{"label":"Ex 14:7","book":"Exo","chapter":14,"verse":7},{"label":"Dt 2:30","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":30},{"label":"Jos 11:20","book":"Jos","chapter":11,"verse":20},{"label":"Jn 12:40","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":40},{"label":"Rm 11:7","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":7},{"label":"Rm 11:25","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You will say to me, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:19","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:25","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:18","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" therefore, “Why then does he still find fault? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:7","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" For who resists his will?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 20:6","book":"2Ch","chapter":20,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 9:12","book":"Job","chapter":9,"verse":12,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 4:35","book":"Dan","chapter":4,"verse":35,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 11:19","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":19},{"label":"1Co 15:25","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":25},{"label":"Jms 2:18","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":18},{"label":"Rm 3:7","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":7},{"label":"2Ch 20:6","book":"2Ch","chapter":20,"verse":6},{"label":"Jb 9:12","book":"Job","chapter":9,"verse":12},{"label":"Dn 4:35","book":"Dan","chapter":4,"verse":35}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On the contrary, who are you, a human being, to talk back to God? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 33:13","book":"Job","chapter":33,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Will what is formed say to the one who formed it, “Why did you make me like this?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 29:16","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 45:9","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 18:6","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 2:20","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 33:13","book":"Job","chapter":33,"verse":13},{"label":"Is 29:16","book":"Isa","chapter":29,"verse":16},{"label":"Is 45:9","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":9},{"label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8},{"label":"Jr 18:6","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":6},{"label":"2Tm 2:20","book":"2Ti","chapter":2,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Or has the potter no right over the clay, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 18:6","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to make from the same lump one piece of pottery for honor and another for dishonor? "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 64:8","book":"Isa","chapter":64,"verse":8},{"label":"Jr 18:6","book":"Jer","chapter":18,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And what if God, wanting to display his wrath and to make his power known, endured with much patience "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:4","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" objects of wrath prepared for destruction? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 16:4","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 2:4","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Pr 16:4","book":"Pro","chapter":16,"verse":4},{"label":"1Pt 2:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom: