Lord will execute his sentence"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And just as Isaiah predicted:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What should we say then? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:14","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Gentiles, who did not pursue righteousness, have obtained righteousness —namely the righteousness that comes from faith. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:17","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:21","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:6","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 2:16","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:24","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":24,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:9","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 11:7","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":7,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 9:14","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 1:17","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":17},{"label":"Rm 3:21","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":21},{"label":"Rm 10:6","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":6},{"label":"Gl 2:16","book":"Gal","chapter":2,"verse":16},{"label":"Gl 3:24","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":24},{"label":"Php 3:9","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Heb 11:7","book":"Heb","chapter":11,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But Israel, pursuing the law of righteousness, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 51:1","book":"Isa","chapter":51,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:2","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 10:20","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:7","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" has not achieved the righteousness of the law. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read the law for righteousness"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:4","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 51:1","book":"Isa","chapter":51,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 10:2","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":2},{"label":"Rm 10:20","book":"Rom","chapter":10,"verse":20},{"label":"Rm 11:7","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":7},{"label":"Gl 5:4","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read the law for righteousness"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Why is that? Because they did not pursue it by faith, but as if it were by works. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add of the law"},{"kind":"text","text":" They stumbled over the stumbling stone. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:6","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Pt 2:6","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"1Pt 2:8","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add of the law"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:9:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As it is written,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099533846}